<l>aḷavu niṟaiyu māyiya ṟiriyātu</l>
<l>kuṟṟiya lukaramum valleḻut tiyaṟkaiyu</l>
<l>muṟkiḷan taṉṉa veṉmaṉār pulavar</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Learned men say that [word denoting] measures and weights do</l>
<l>not deviate from the above rules; over-short <foreign xml:lang="ta">u</foreign> and the plosive [<foreign xml:lang="ta">ṟṟ</foreign>]</l>
<l>are the same as before.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
